<plot>This story about two maternal half-brothers, a Croat and a Serb. Although they never met, and both lose their loved ones in ethnic clashes, there is a bond between them. Filmed in 1988, "Braca po materi" prophetically forsees the war that would engulf former Yugoslavia three years later.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?081419</url></doc>
